sentences: Co Streiff (Cornelia Streiff) (5 April 1959 in Zurich) is a Swiss jazz musician who combines the elements of free jazz with the music of Africa.
In 1986, she began her collaboration with Irène Schweizer.
Co Streiff – Irène Schweizer: Twin Lines (Intakt Records 2002)
Co Streiff Sextet: Loops, Holes & Angels (Inakt Records 2007)
